{"tid":647019,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《再見螢火蟲》若非反戰片……","createTime":"2018-04-29T13:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T11:11:39.000Z","uid":130591,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa2b0230e87565de33af60cc5252bb1e093d3233","tid":647019,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:46:21.000Z","msg":"第一次看是在初中時，那時看電影容易被畫面感染，睇到最尾喊左出嚟。<br />\n過了一段時間也不敢看。大學時偶爾又無聊看看，開始留意其中的細節，在思索悲慘嘅結局背後嘅原因何在，那時便已注意到，其實個妹嘅死係受哥哥「太爭氣」連累所致，轉折位係離開阿姨獨自求生開始。<br />\n剛才J2重播，令我事隔多年後為這齣戲上網爬文。找找看看，就找到wiki資料及一篇甚得我心嘅影評－其實導演高畑勳不是要要帶出反戰思想，呢齣戲嘅主題，其實在於諷刺日本新生代的社會狀況：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/l/OFL01qCG?bk_share=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbaike.baidu.com%2Fl%2FOFL01qCG%3Fbk_share%3Dcopy&d=sSYdjU7C7ik4kpV3FL79f1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=2ccc19a2\" target=\"_blank\">http://baike.baidu.com/l/OFL01qCG?bk_share=copy</a><br />\n<br />\n高汁分析！大陸好多人批判齣戲「沒有完全反省侵略惡行」，反日反上腦，呢位影評人可謂一下打醒佢地。<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，《再見螢火蟲》仍是我心目中最高汁嘅動畫片！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3910ec9c8c2c128ca824af8e3f49330ff7f6e3c","tid":647019,"uid":43523,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T14:01:19.000Z","msg":"Nii-chan~~~<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/891a4117b123b1dcbca85d40bdae364c/tumblr_nhiu5sA1bl1rll7syo1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F891a4117b123b1dcbca85d40bdae364c%2Ftumblr_nhiu5sA1bl1rll7syo1_500.gif&h=b0456491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/44053a68b7359c91fa59ffb4589754c5/tumblr_n1wbtgEaX41rmvkpdo2_r1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F44053a68b7359c91fa59ffb4589754c5%2Ftumblr_n1wbtgEaX41rmvkpdo2_r1_500.gif&h=500b0c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/224525474/original.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whic